# Build artifacts / models.
# The /models/ directory holds large binary model files that are never committed.
# shared/models/ is source code and IS tracked — /models/ is anchored to the root.
# manifest.json.example is the committed structure template; it was added with
# git add -f (the only reliable way to track a file inside an otherwise-ignored
# tree — gitignore ! exceptions cannot override a parent-directory ignore rule).
# manifest.json (the real per-machine digest file) is per-machine, never committed.
/models/
/models/qwen3-14b/openvino-int4-gpu/manifest.json
dist/
build/

